            "creation_date": 1417785861,
            "body": "<p>Try below code:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String sql = \"SELECT expiray_time FROM recover_password WHERE token = ?\";\n\nObject[] args = new Object[] {//token object};\nObject obj = getJdbcTemplate().queryForObject(sql, args, java.sql.Timestamp);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>or try this:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String sql = \"SELECT expiray_time FROM recover_password WHERE token = \"+token;\njava.sql.Timestamp ex_time = getJdbcTemplate().queryForObject(sql, new Object[] { token } , java.sql.Timestamp);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
